title: $5000-4/2.5 Hollywood 2 Story House-Immaculate Custom/Modern Upgrades
neighborhood: Hollywood - West of I-95 - Maple Ridge
posting_body: ['Beautiful Fully Updated and Spacious 3 Bedroom + Bonus Room, 2.5 Bathroom, 2 Story House in the Highly Desired Gated Community of Maple Ridge.', 'Corner Lot, Updated Kitchen with Island Bar, Wall Oven and All Stainless Steel Appliances.', 'Laundry Room is Located Just Off the 2 Car Car Garage and Features a Top Loader Washer and Dryer.', 'Master Bedroom has a Huge Walk-In Closet with Custom Shelving.', 'Large Master Bathroom with Jacuzzi and Separate Shower.', 'The Fenced Backyard has a Lovely Huge Patio, Great for Entertaining Friends and Family.', 'So Many Upgrades.', 'Entire Home is Freshly Painted White.', "Maple Ridge has a Community Pool, Children's Playground.", 'It is Located Between I-95 & the Turnpike, Close to International Ft Lauderdale Airport, walking distance to houses of worship and Hard Rock Casino.', 'Pets ok with landlord approval.', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease (650+), background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
